### Create a new poll
POST http://localhost:3000/polls
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "What's your favorite programming language?",
  "options": ["JavaScript", "Python", "Java", "C#", "Go"]
}

### Get all polls
GET http://localhost:3000/polls

### Get a specific poll
GET http://localhost:3000/polls/1

### Vote for an option (replace optionId with actual ID from poll response)
POST http://localhost:3000/polls/1/vote
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "optionId": "replace-with-actual-option-id"
} 